quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  86,1,By the sky and the Taariq
  86,2,And what will make you realize what Taariq is
  86,3,(It is) the piercing star
  86,4,There is not a single soul which does not have a custodian over it
  86,5,So let man see from what he was created
  86,6,He was created from gushing water (fluid)
  86,7,that comes out from in between the loins and the ribs
  86,8,"He is certainly able to return him, (and make him face)"
  86,9,"the day, (when) secrets will be examined"
  86,10,then there will neither be strength nor a helper for him
  86,11,By the sky that returns (the water in the form of rain)
  86,12,and the earth that splits (due to vegetation)
  86,13,this (Quran) is certainly a decisive statement
  86,14,and it is not (something to be taken as) a joke
  86,15,They certainly plot a plot
  86,16,and I (too) plot a plot
  86,17,"So give time to the disbelievers, give them time for a while"